column5:
Update publish_data.yaml

{{ system.domain }}  =>>  {{ st2kv.system.domain }}    
After V2.2 ,this is not supported.

Rename 'action' field to 'ref' in Rule

Before the change:

Rule:
{
  trigger: {},
  action: {
    action: 'pack.action_name',
    parameters: {}
  }
}

After the change:

Rule:
{
  trigger: {},
  action: {
    ref: 'pack.action_name',
    parameters: {}
  }
}
